{"tid":689931,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人食過嗰間乜撚野加藤屋?","createTime":"2018-06-04T12:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T13:50:58.000Z","uid":183601,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"834fd1984049dfcfd5b10d99ad7f36d54a968faf","tid":689931,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"老翻吉野家, 之前食過1-2次<br />\n話說今日day off 落樓求其食個下午茶餐<br />\n叫咗個雞飯, $25蚊咁<br />\n之前食過佢d雞汁就好撚柒鳩難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌老尾食落口成陣藥油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都會叫佢比碗牛肉汁<br />\n用牛肉汁嚟送先食到<br />\n<br />\n今日如是者落order走汁, 再去水吧叫佢比碗牛肉汁啦<br />\n點知佢話而家公司新規定雞飯只可配雞汁, 牛飯只可配牛汁<br />\n我屌你老母你間垃圾扮乜撚嘢上菜呀<br />\n本身間野扮吉野家, 扮日本野已經on撚9<br />\n應該支那野啦, 唔係點會抄鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個場又拍烏蠅<br />\n野又難撚食, 唔係你個汁難撚食我駛撚轉汁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰兩羹汁都喺度計<br />\n隔離其他食店得佢一間咁撚頹真係有原因<br />\n以後比多幾蚊食隔離<br />\n執柒咗去啦屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"548086dddb6d64e36c1602f353f468db7629576b","tid":689931,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57abad3c6e9f762847b97c78e60c742520e1d909","tid":689931,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"548086dddb6d64e36c1602f353f468db7629576b","tid":689931,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"唔知wor, 好少食無留意<br />\n比人起咗底?"},{"pid":"2773db4723d6a093cfc7e41f19cabc3a78d341ef","tid":689931,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"25蚊咁抵?"},{"pid":"42b3cefa1faec095f3e79adbe2e8333b6d6bb39a","tid":689931,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45e7ce922fb619bc8292db746f8c4597ae88748e","tid":689931,"uid":164836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"思覺失調"},{"pid":"8a74a0587f26d00813085f3698a56acb4b60767f","tid":689931,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"之前粉嶺有間長期拍污蠅<br />\n好似特登開嚟洗錢咁"},{"pid":"0b2825afed2e3b9843104a3764fec816693d1167","tid":689931,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:27:20.000Z","msg":"係譚仔黎嘅"},{"pid":"426c348033b8d2116521be726d190b8d2ebca567","tid":689931,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e7ce922fb619bc8292db746f8c4597ae88748e","tid":689931,"uid":164836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"思覺失調"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"乜野?"},{"pid":"689815384d4f38688958cb572daada1841e6777b","tid":689931,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾都有打手入嚟比負皮!?<br />\n唔撚係呀嘛"},{"pid":"efdd95dff5e257c3ac0746ccc75481ca9ed1db05","tid":689931,"uid":99086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a74a0587f26d00813085f3698a56acb4b60767f","tid":689931,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"之前粉嶺有間長期拍污蠅<br />\n好似特登開嚟洗錢咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"琴日去睇好似收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca806ba562a5a29b28d91ae19c66c8c881859958","tid":689931,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efdd95dff5e257c3ac0746ccc75481ca9ed1db05","tid":689931,"uid":99086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a74a0587f26d00813085f3698a56acb4b60767f","tid":689931,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"之前粉嶺有間長期拍污蠅<br />\n好似特登開嚟洗錢咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T17: